---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Adrienne Kovacs | Talent Strategy Partner for Founders"
  description="Learn about KovaCo., a talent strategy practice by Adrienne Kovacs. We design high-impact recruitment architecture, hiring infrastructure, and executive search systems for early- and growth-stage companies."
>

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-inner">
      <div class="reveal-group">
        <p class="page-eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1 class="page-heading">I'm Adrienne.<br><em>I run KovaCo.</em></h1>
        <p class="page-header-lead">
          Hiring is how a company decides what it is going to become.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="page-header-portrait reveal">
        <img
          src="/adrienne-kovacs.jpg"
          alt="Adrienne Kovacs, founder of KovaCo. Consulting"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- BODY -->
  <main class="about-body-wrap">
    <div class="about-content">

      <!-- Intro -->
      <div class="about-section reveal">
        <p class="about-text">
          For an early- or growth-stage company, the traditional mechanics of recruitment
          frequently break down. Founders are forced to choose between legacy, bureaucratic
          HR frameworks that slow down momentum, or hyper-reactive agencies that fill seats
          without building internal capability.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text about-text--emphasis">
          <a href="https://kovaco.ca">KovaCo.</a> is a talent strategy practice designed for
          the space between: we help founders build foundational hiring systems, run critical
          senior searches, and engineer talent infrastructure that compounds as the business
          grows.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Intersection section -->
      <div class="about-section reveal">
        <p class="section-heading">The Intersection of Strategy and Operational Reality</p>

        <p class="about-text">
          The practice was founded by <strong>Adrienne Kovacs</strong>, whose perspective sits
          at a rare intersection: fifteen years navigating some of the most complex
          institutional hiring environments in British Columbia, alongside the real-world
          experience of building a company from the ground up.
        </p>

        <!-- ─── Paradox profile diagram ───────────────────────────── -->
        <div class="paradox-diagram">
          <img
            src="/kovaco-paradox-profile.svg"
            alt="The KovaCo Paradox Profile Blueprint: Displaying the convergence of Adrienne Kovacs' 15-year strategic institutional scaling framework and real-world operational founder background."
            class="paradox-diagram__img"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>

        <p class="about-text">
          Adrienne entered the recruitment space through the University of British Columbia,
          later completing a post-graduate designation in Human Resources Management to master
          the structured mechanics of workforce planning, assessment data, and organizational
          design.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          However, her understanding of talent fundamentally changed when she became an
          operator herself.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          As the <strong>founder of Locum Home Inc.</strong>, a specialized workforce housing
          platform serving healthcare professionals, she experienced the acute pressures of
          scaling a lean business. She validated the market, acquired the initial
          infrastructure, and successfully <strong>headhunted her own co-founder</strong> to
          join the vision before formally registering the BC Incorporation.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          Building a business while advising others on talent erased the division between
          theoretical HR and operational truth. It proved that growing companies do not need
          rigid, administrative policies; they need clear data, repeatable decision frameworks,
          and an aggressive focus on alignment. KovaCo. is where those two worlds converge.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tested under complexity -->
      <div class="about-section reveal">
        <p class="section-heading">Tested Under Complexity</p>
        <p class="about-text">
          To build talent architecture that survives rapid scaling, systems must first be
          stress-tested where the margins for error are thinnest.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          Adrienne spent more than a decade designing and steering recruitment infrastructure
          across Western Canada's most high-volume, highly regulated, and high-stakes sectors:
        </p>
        <ul class="about-list">
          <li>
            <strong>System Scale:</strong> Directing international pipeline strategies and
            executive recruitment for critical medical leadership roles across expansive
            geographic footprints.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Structural Alignment:</strong> Developing structured, objective hiring
            systems for public healthcare, post-secondary institutions, and Indigenous-led
            organizations — environments where compliance, bias elimination, and long-term
            retention are paramount.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Data Architecture:</strong> Replacing recruitment intuition with rigorous
            analytics. Adrienne builds data structures and live pipeline dashboards that reveal
            precisely where a company's hiring process creates drag, allowing founders to make
            talent decisions based on metrics rather than guesswork.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Strategic interventions -->
      <div class="about-section reveal">
        <p class="section-heading">Strategic Interventions</p>
        <p class="about-text">
          We work with founders and people leaders to build talent capability before growth
          exposes the lack of it. The practice engages across three specific pillars:
        </p>
        <ul class="about-list about-list--pillars">
          <li>
            <strong>01 — Audit:</strong> A structured, objective review of how your company
            currently hires to locate where decisions break down and where process creates
            operational drag.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>02 — Build:</strong> Designing the custom hiring capability your team will
            run long-term, including structured interview frameworks, candidate scorecards, and
            employer positioning.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>03 — Advise:</strong> Ongoing strategic guidance for founders navigating
            organizational changes, scaling thresholds, or high-stakes leadership decisions.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="about-text about-text--note">
          <em>Senior and specialized executive searches are also undertaken as standalone
          strategic engagements.</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Equity block -->
      <div class="equity-block reveal">
        <p class="equity-label">On equity &amp; accessibility</p>
        <p class="equity-text">Equitable hiring isn't a service line at KovaCo. — it's a default. I bring ongoing training in Indigenous Cultural Safety, direct experience designing recruitment for an Indigenous-led organization expanding across BC, and a working understanding of how to build hiring systems that are accessible by design rather than retrofitted later.</p>
        <p class="equity-text">The companies I partner with are ones that take this seriously. The ones that don't, won't be a fit.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- TESTIMONIAL -->
  <div class="testimonial-block reveal">
    <div class="testimonial-block-inner">
      <div class="testimonial-quote-mark" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
      <blockquote class="testimonial-snippet">
        Adrienne built the tools and systems necessary to support our rapid expansion… She brings a strong, strategic project management lens to her work and excels at building relationships. Businesses expanding across the country would be lucky to have her.
      </blockquote>
      <footer class="testimonial-footer">
        <div class="testimonial-meta">
          <p class="testimonial-author">Amanda Carling, JD</p>
          <p class="testimonial-role">Former CEO / Co-Founder</p>
          <p class="testimonial-company">BC First Nations Justice Council / Canadian Registry of Wrongful Convictions</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/impact/amanda-carling" class="testimonial-link">Read the full story →</a>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- LOCATION -->
  <div class="location-strip">
    <div class="location-inner">
      <p class="location-label">Location</p>
      <p class="location-text">Based in Vernon, in the Okanagan, on the unceded territory of the syilx Okanagan people. Most work is remote, with travel for engagements that call for it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta">
    <p class="about-cta-eyebrow">Design your foundational team</p>
    <p class="about-cta-headline">The first ten hires dictate the trajectory of an enterprise.</p>
    <p class="about-cta-sub">
      Leaving those decisions to chance, legacy checklists, or external vendors who do not
      understand your architecture creates hidden organizational debt. Let's build a talent
      system designed for what your company is becoming.
    </p>
    <a href="https://calendly.com/hello-kovaco/30min" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      Book an intro call <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </a>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ─── Page header ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .page-header {
    padding: 100px 40px 80px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .page-header-inner {
    max-width: var(--max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 72px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .page-heading {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5.5vw, 74px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-top: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .page-heading em { font-style: italic; }
  .page-header-lead {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 22px);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--mid);
    max-width: 46ch;
  }

  .page-header-portrait {
    position: relative;
    background: rgba(143,160,136,0.08);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    max-height: 620px;
    justify-self: end;
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .page-header-portrait img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
  }

  /* ─── Body content ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .about-body-wrap {
    padding: 100px 40px;
  }
  .about-content {
    max-width: var(--col);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }
  .about-section:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .about-text {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .about-text:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .about-text strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
  .about-text a {
    color: var(--text);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sage);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .about-text a:hover { color: var(--sage); }
  .about-text--emphasis {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .about-text--note { margin-top: 20px; }

  /* ─── About list ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .about-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .about-list li {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--mid);
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .about-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 12px;
    width: 6px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--sage);
  }
  .about-list li strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }

  .about-list--pillars {
    counter-reset: pillars;
  }
  .about-list--pillars li {
    padding-left: 0;
  }
  .about-list--pillars li::before { display: none; }

  /* ─── Paradox profile diagram ───────────────────────────────── */
  .paradox-diagram {
    margin-block: 48px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .paradox-diagram__img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 720px;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ─── Pull quote ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pull-quote {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--sage);
    padding: 4px 0 4px 32px;
    margin: 48px 0;
  }
  .pull-quote p {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* ─── Equity block ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .equity-block {
    background: var(--text);
    color: var(--bg);
    padding: 52px;
    margin: 72px 0;
  }
  .equity-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage-light);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .equity-text {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(245,242,237,0.85);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-width: 100%;
  }
  .equity-text:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* ─── Testimonial block ──────────────────────────────────────── */
  .testimonial-block {
    padding: 0 40px 80px;
  }
  .testimonial-block-inner {
    max-width: var(--col);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 48px 52px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
  }
  .testimonial-quote-mark {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 72px;
    line-height: 0.6;
    color: var(--sage);
    opacity: 0.45;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .testimonial-snippet {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 21px);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text);
    quotes: none;
  }
  .testimonial-footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .testimonial-author {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .testimonial-role  { font-size: 13px; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .testimonial-company { font-size: 12px; color: var(--sage); letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
  .testimonial-link {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .testimonial-link:hover { color: var(--sage); border-color: var(--sage); }

  /* ─── Location strip ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .location-strip {
    padding: 64px 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .location-inner {
    max-width: var(--col);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .location-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .location-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--mid);
  }

  /* ─── Closing CTA ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .about-cta {
    padding: 120px 40px;
    text-align: center;
    display: grid;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-items: center;
  }
  .about-cta-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
  }
  .about-cta-headline {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--text);
    max-width: 22ch;
  }
  .about-cta-sub {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--mid);
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  /* ─── Responsive ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .page-header { padding: 72px 24px 64px; }
    .page-header-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .page-header-portrait {
      width: min(100%, 360px);
      max-height: 460px;
    }
    .about-body-wrap     { padding: 72px 24px; }
    .location-strip      { padding: 64px 24px; }
    .location-inner      { flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .about-cta           { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .equity-block        { padding: 36px 28px; }
    .testimonial-block   { padding: 0 24px 64px; }
    .testimonial-block-inner { padding: 36px 28px; }
    .testimonial-footer  { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }

  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .page-heading { font-size: 36px; }
  }
</style>
